## 2026-03-28 - ResolverPanel contextual help and starter templates
- Added "Light / Dark preset" template button to the empty state "Get started" section (dashed border to distinguish it as a template). Clicking it shows a name-input creation form with a "foundation + mode modifier" label. The template creates a resolver with foundation/light/dark sets (auto-detecting set names containing "light"/"dark"/"foundation"/"base"/"global" from existing sets) and a `mode` modifier with `light`/`dark` contexts wired to `#/sets/light` and `#/sets/dark` in the resolution order.
